### 4. CATERING FUNCTION SUPERIORITY: 4/10
**Problems:**
- No interactive menu builder that allows real-time customization
- No event calculator for different guest counts and dietary needs
- No integration with popular Russian food delivery platforms
- Package comparison lacks detailed breakdowns
- No virtual consultation booking system

**Specific Fixes:**
```tsx
