### 5. MOBILE EXPERIENCE: 7/10
**Problems:**
- Bottom nav is good but lacks swipe gestures
- Touch targets are adequate but not generous enough
- Cart sheet doesn't fully utilize mobile screen real estate
- Menu preview grid doesn't adapt well to vertical scrolling

**Specific Fixes:**
```tsx
// Enhance mobile navigation with gestures
const MobileNav = () => {
  const [activeIndex, setActiveIndex] = useState(0);

  return (
    <nav className="mobile-nav">
