### 6. MENU BUILDER UX: 6/10
**Problems:**
- No visual representation of how dishes complement each other
- No allergen cross-referencing system
- No nutritional information beyond БЖУ
- No save/share menu functionality
- No price adjustment based on seasonal availability

**Specific Fixes:**
```tsx
// Implement comprehensive menu builder
const MenuBuilder = () => {
  const [selectedItems, setSelectedItems] = useState([]);
  const [guestProfile, setGuestProfile] = useState({
    dietaryRestrictions: [],
