        <MenuSummary items={selectedItems} />
        <CompatibilityMatrix items={selectedItems} />
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
```

### 7. CONVERSION OPTIMIZATION: 5/10
**Problems:**
- CTAs are generic ("Рассчитать стоимость") without urgency
- No social proof beyond basic testimonials
- No scarcity indicators (limited packages, seasonal offers)
- No exit-intent popups for abandoned carts
- WhatsApp integration is just a button, not a conversation starter

**Specific Fixes:**
```tsx
