### 8. CONTENT QUALITY: 7/10
**Problems:**
- Blog posts lack depth and frequency
- Testimonials don't showcase specific results or metrics
- No case studies with before/after photos
- Menu descriptions are basic without storytelling elements
- No chef profiles or culinary philosophy

**Specific Fixes:**
